data.name: Label6.Text
data.value: Hilton Cairo Heliopolis, located near Cairo International Airport, offers two outdoor pools, a children's pool, a fitness center, squash courts, and 13 restaurants. Rooms feature Egyptian-themed decor, air conditioning, flat-screen TVs, and mini-bars, with some offering pool views. The hotel also has a casino and a sports bar. It's highly rated by couples for its convenient location, just 3.1 miles from the airport.
